articles.title: Australia banned social media for under 16s a month ago — here's how it's going - CNBC
articles.description: The effects of a new social media ban for under 16s in Australia has been mixed so far. Some teens are embracing new habits while others are bypassing the law.
articles.content:
A notification on the Instagram app on a smartphone arranged in Sydney, Australia, on Thursday, Dec. 4, 2025.
